    <item>
      <title>高盛的奥本海默表示，科技股抛售不会改变美国例外论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/tech-selloff-doesn-t-change-us-exceptionalism-says-goldman-s-oppenheimer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席全球股票策略师彼得·奥本海默 (Peter Oppenheimer) 表示，科技股的抛售并没有真正改变“根本的基本面”，因为美国和全球经济的基础“仍然对市场，尤其是科技行业具有相当大的支撑作用”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/tech-selloff-doesn-t-change-us-exceptionalism-says-goldman-s-oppenheimer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 11:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典将再次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/sweden-is-set-to-cut-interest-rates-again-decision-day-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行本周可能会下调借贷成本，此举可能是该行为帮助欧洲表现最弱的经济体之一实现增长而采取的最后一项举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/sweden-is-set-to-cut-interest-rates-again-decision-day-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国银行缩减贷款 导致汽车销量跌至 14 年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国国内汽车销量跌至 15 年来的最低水平，损害了其作为“亚洲底特律”的声誉，因为银行贷款审批收紧和家庭债务高企导致汽车需求受到挤压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:21:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能行业动荡导致比特币下跌，为加密货币涨势蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 引发的全球市场动荡导致了数字资产的波动，继去年价格暴涨之后，人们对加密货币的前景产生了新的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 02:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁征收关税后，美国铜价上涨，伦敦铜价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/copper-extends-losses-after-trump-threatens-tariffs-on-metals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普承诺征收进口关税，此举有可能提高美国制造商的成本，同时抑制全球需求，导致铜价在纽约上涨，在伦敦下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/copper-extends-losses-after-trump-threatens-tariffs-on-metals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 01:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
